<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
<title>런뉴 - 마라톤 & 러닝 대회</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700;900&family=Bebas+Neue&family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --bg: #0d0d0f;
    --surface: #161619;
    --surface2: #1e1e23;
    --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    --text: #f0f0f2;
    --text-muted: #7a7a8a;
    --accent: #e8f000;
    --accent2: #ff4d2e;
    --accent3: #00c9a7;
    --radius: 16px;
    --tab-h: 60px;
  }

  html, body {
    height: 100%;
    background: #000;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-start;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
  }

  /* ── Phone Shell ── */
  #phone {
    width: 390px;
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: var(--bg);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  /* ── Status Bar ── */
  .status-bar {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 14px 20px 6px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .status-icons { display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center; font-size: 12px; }

  /* ── Screens ── */
  .screen { display: none; flex-direction: column; flex: 1; overflow: hidden; }
  .screen.active { display: flex; }

  /* ── Tab Bar ── */
  .tab-bar {
    display: flex;
    background: var(--surface);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    height: var(--tab-h);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .tab-btn {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 3px;
    border: none;
    background: none;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: color .2s;
  }
  .tab-btn.active { color: var(--accent); }
  .tab-btn svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; }

  /* ══════════════════════════════
     SCREEN 1 · 대회 목록
  ══════════════════════════════ */
  #screen-list { background: var(--bg); }

  /* Hero */
  .list-hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 200px;
    overflow: hidden;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .list-hero img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;
    filter: brightness(.55);
  }
  .list-hero-overlay {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 30%, var(--bg) 100%);
  }
  .list-hero-content {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 20px; left: 20px; right: 20px;
  }
  .list-hero-content h1 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 38px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .list-hero-content h1 span { color: var(--accent); }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.6);
    margin-top: 4px;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* Filter chips */
  .filter-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .filter-row::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  .chip {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--surface2);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all .2s;
  }
  .chip.active {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #000;
    border-color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* Sort row */
  .sort-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 4px 16px 10px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .sort-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .sort-label strong { color: var(--text); }
  .sort-btn {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  /* Race list */
  .race-list {
    flex: 1;
    overflow-y: auto;
    padding: 0 16px 16px;
  }
  .race-list::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

  /* Race card */
  .race-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 14px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all .2s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .race-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0;
    width: 3px;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 3px 0 0 3px;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity .2s;
  }
  .race-card:active { transform: scale(.98); }
  .race-card:active::before { opacity: 1; }

  .race-date-box {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 48px;
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--surface2);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 8px 4px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .race-date-box .month {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .race-date-box .day {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .race-date-box .dow {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .race-info { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .race-badges { display: flex; gap: 5px; margin-bottom: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .badge {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 2px 7px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    letter-spacing: .5px;
  }
  .badge-full { background: rgba(232,240,0,.15); color: var(--accent); border: 1px solid rgba(232,240,0,.3); }
  .badge-half { background: rgba(0,201,167,.15); color: var(--accent3); border: 1px solid rgba(0,201,167,.3); }
  .badge-10k { background: rgba(255,77,46,.15); color: var(--accent2); border: 1px solid rgba(255,77,46,.3); }
  .badge-trail { background: rgba(120,100,255,.15); color: #a88fff; border: 1px solid rgba(120,100,255,.3); }
  .badge-new { background: var(--accent2); color: #fff; }

  .race-title {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
  }
  .race-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .race-meta span { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 3px; }

  .race-right {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .d-day {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }
  .d-day.open { background: rgba(232,240,0,.15); color: var(--accent); }
  .d-day.close { background: var(--surface2); color: var(--text-muted); }
  .d-day.soon { background: rgba(255,77,46,.15); color: var(--accent2); }

  .participants-bar {
    width: 60px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--surface2);
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .participants-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent3), var(--accent));
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .participants-text {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: 3px;
    text-align: right;
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════
     SCREEN 2 · 대회 상세
  ══════════════════════════════ */
  #screen-detail { background: var(--bg); }

  .detail-scroll { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; }
  .detail-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

  /* Detail hero */
  .detail-hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 240px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .detail-hero img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;
    filter: brightness(.6);
  }
  .detail-hero-overlay {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,.3) 0%, var(--bg) 100%);
  }
  .detail-back {
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px; left: 16px;
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,.5);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }
  .detail-wishlist {
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px; right: 16px;
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,.5);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .detail-hero-content {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 20px; left: 20px; right: 20px;
  }
  .detail-hero-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    line-height: 1.1;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.5);
  }

  /* Detail body */
  .detail-body { padding: 20px; }

  /* Course tabs */
  .course-tabs {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .course-tab {
    padding: 8px 18px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all .2s;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
  }
  .course-tab.active { background: var(--accent); color: #000; }
  .course-tab:not(.active) { background: var(--surface2); color: var(--text-muted); border: 1px solid var(--border); }

  /* Info grid */
  .info-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .info-item {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 14px;
  }
  .info-item .label {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: .8px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px;
  }
  .info-item .value {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .info-item .value small {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .info-item.accent-border { border-color: rgba(232,240,0,.3); }

  /* Section */
  .section { margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .section-title {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  }
  .section-title::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  /* Timeline */
  .timeline { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
  .tl-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    padding-bottom: 16px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .tl-item:not(:last-child)::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 16px; top: 30px; bottom: 0;
    width: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
  }
  .tl-dot {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 32px; height: 32px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .tl-dot.done { background: rgba(232,240,0,.15); border-color: rgba(232,240,0,.4); }
  .tl-content .tl-date { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .tl-content .tl-label { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }

  /* Course badges large */
  .course-badges {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .course-badge-lg {
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .course-badge-lg.f { background: rgba(232,240,0,.15); color: var(--accent); border: 1px solid rgba(232,240,0,.3); }
  .course-badge-lg.h { background: rgba(0,201,167,.15); color: var(--accent3); border: 1px solid rgba(0,201,167,.3); }
  .course-badge-lg.t { background: rgba(120,100,255,.15); color: #a88fff; border: 1px solid rgba(120,100,255,.3); }

  /* Contact */
  .contact-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 12px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .contact-icon {
    width: 32px; height: 32px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--surface2);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 16px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .contact-text { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }

  /* Description box */
  .desc-box {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(240,240,242,.75);
  }
  .desc-box p { margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .desc-box p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .desc-highlight {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .desc-highlight .icon { flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }

  /* CTA bar */
  .cta-bar {
    position: sticky;
    bottom: 0;
    padding: 12px 20px 24px;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, var(--bg) 70%, transparent);
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .cta-share {
    width: 48px; height: 48px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--surface);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .cta-register {
    flex: 1;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: var(--accent);
    border: none;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #000;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
    transition: all .2s;
  }
  .cta-register:active { transform: scale(.97); }

  /* ══════════════════════════════
     SCREEN 3 · 지도 / 일정
  ══════════════════════════════ */
  #screen-calendar { background: var(--bg); }

  .cal-header {
    padding: 16px 20px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .cal-header h2 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .cal-header h2 span { color: var(--accent); }

  .cal-month-nav {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0 20px 12px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .cal-month-nav button {
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
    width: 32px; height: 32px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 16px;
  }
  .cal-month-nav .month-label {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .cal-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr);
    padding: 0 16px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .cal-dow {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    padding: 4px 0;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .cal-day {
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    border-radius: 10px;
    position: relative;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .cal-day.current-month { color: var(--text); }
  .cal-day.today {
    background: var(--surface2);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .cal-day .race-dot {
    width: 4px; height: 4px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 3px;
  }
  .cal-day .race-dot.red { background: var(--accent2); }

  .upcoming-list {
    flex: 1;
    overflow-y: auto;
    padding: 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
  .upcoming-list::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

  .upcoming-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 12px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .upcoming-stripe {
    width: 4px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .upcoming-stripe.yellow { background: var(--accent); }
  .upcoming-stripe.red { background: var(--accent2); }
  .upcoming-stripe.teal { background: var(--accent3); }
  .upcoming-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .upcoming-meta { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); }

  /* ══════════════════════════════
     SCREEN 4 · 마이페이지
  ══════════════════════════════ */
  #screen-my { background: var(--bg); overflow-y: auto; }

  .my-scroll { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; }
  .my-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

  .my-profile {
    padding: 24px 20px 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .avatar {
    width: 64px; height: 64px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent3));
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    color: #000;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .profile-info .name {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .profile-info .email {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .profile-info .level {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    margin-top: 6px;
    background: rgba(232,240,0,.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(232,240,0,.3);
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .stats-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 0 20px 20px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .stat-box {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 14px 10px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat-unit { font-size: 12px; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; }
  .stat-label { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 4px; }

  .my-section { padding: 0 20px 20px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .my-section-title {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .my-menu-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 14px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .my-menu-icon {
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: var(--surface2);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 18px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .my-menu-label { flex: 1; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }
  .my-menu-arrow { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 16px; }

  /* Animations */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .screen.active .race-card,
  .screen.active .info-item,
  .screen.active .detail-body > * {
    animation: fadeUp .35s ease both;
  }
  .race-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0ms; }
  .race-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 50ms; }
  .race-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 100ms; }
  .race-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 150ms; }
  .race-card:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 200ms; }
  .race-card:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 250ms; }

  @media (max-width: 420px) {
    #phone { width: 100%; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="phone">
  <div class="status-bar">
    <span>9:30</span>
    <div class="status-icons">
      <svg width="16" height="12" viewBox="0 0 16 12" fill="currentColor"><rect x="0" y="3" width="3" height="9" rx="1"/><rect x="4" y="2" width="3" height="10" rx="1"/><rect x="8" y="0" width="3" height="12" rx="1"/><rect x="12" y="0" width="3" height="12" rx="1" opacity=".3"/></svg>
      <svg width="16" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 12" fill="currentColor"><path d="M1 4C5.5.5 18.5.5 23 4M4.5 7.5C7.5 5 16.5 5 19.5 7.5M8 11c2-1.5 6-1.5 8 0M12 14v.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
      <span style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;">87%</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ══ SCREEN 1: 목록 ══ -->
  <div class="screen active" id="screen-list">
    <div class="list-hero">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1530549387789-4c1017266635?w=800&q=80" alt="마라톤">
      <div class="list-hero-overlay"></div>
      <div class="list-hero-content">
        <h1>RUN <span>NOW</span></h1>
        <div class="hero-sub">국내 · 해외 런닝화 페이스 계산</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="filter-row">
      <div class="chip active">전체</div>
      <div class="chip">마라톤</div>
      <div class="chip">하프</div>
      <div class="chip">10K</div>
      <div class="chip">5K</div>
      <div class="chip">트레일</div>
      <div class="chip">인제</div>
      <div class="chip">경기</div>
      <div class="chip">서울</div>
    </div>

    <div class="sort-row">
      <span class="sort-label">대회 목록 <strong>총 128개</strong></span>
      <button class="sort-btn">날짜순 ▾</button>
    </div>

    <div class="race-list">
      <!-- 카드 1 -->
      <div class="race-card" onclick="showDetail()">
        <div class="race-date-box">
          <div class="month">APR</div>
          <div class="day">3</div>
          <div class="dow">목</div>
        </div>
        <div class="race-info">
          <div class="race-badges">
            <span class="badge badge-trail">TRAIL</span>
            <span class="badge badge-new">NEW</span>
          </div>
          <div class="race-title">2026 장수트레일레이스 Spring</div>
          <div class="race-meta">
            <span>📍 전북 장수</span>
            <span>70K · 38K · 20K</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="race-right">
          <div class="d-day open">접수중</div>
          <div>
            <div class="participants-bar"><div class="participants-fill" style="width:72%"></div></div>
            <div class="participants-text">72%</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 카드 2 -->
      <div class="race-card" onclick="showDetail()">
        <div class="race-date-box">
          <div class="month">APR</div>
          <div class="day">5</div>
          <div class="dow">일</div>
        </div>
        <div class="race-info">
          <div class="race-badges">
            <span class="badge badge-full">FULL</span>
            <span class="badge badge-half">HALF</span>
          </div>
          <div class="race-title">수원 공굴산마라톤</div>
          <div class="race-meta">
            <span>📍 경기 수원</span>
            <span>42K · 21K</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="race-right">
          <div class="d-day soon">D-3</div>
          <div>
            <div class="participants-bar"><div class="participants-fill" style="width:91%"></div></div>
            <div class="participants-text">91%</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 카드 3 -->
      <div class="race-card" onclick="showDetail()">
        <div class="race-date-box">
          <div class="month">APR</div>
          <div class="day">6</div>
          <div class="dow">월</div>
        </div>
        <div class="race-info">
          <div class="race-badges">
            <span class="badge badge-full">FULL</span>
            <span class="badge badge-10k">10K</span>
          </div>
          <div class="race-title">오크밸리 봄 스나트 레이스</div>
          <div class="race-meta">
            <span>📍 강원 원주</span>
            <span>42K · 10K · 5K</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="race-right">
          <div class="d-day open">접수중</div>
          <div>
            <div class="participants-bar"><div class="participants-fill" style="width:45%"></div></div>
            <div class="participants-text">45%</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 카드 4 -->
      <div class="race-card" onclick="showDetail()">
        <div class="race-date-box">
          <div class="month">APR</div>
          <div class="day">12</div>
          <div class="dow">일</div>
        </div>
        <div class="race-info">
          <div class="race-badges">
            <span class="badge badge-full">FULL</span>
            <span class="badge badge-half">HALF</span>
            <span class="badge badge-10k">10K</span>
          </div>
          <div class="race-title">2026 글로벌 건양대학교 K-국제 마라톤</div>
          <div class="race-meta">
            <span>📍 충남 논산</span>
            <span>42K · 21K · 10K</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="race-right">
          <div class="d-day open">접수중</div>
          <div>
            <div class="participants-bar"><div class="participants-fill" style="width:58%"></div></div>
            <div class="participants-text">58%</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 카드 5 -->
      <div class="race-card" onclick="showDetail()">
        <div class="race-date-box">
          <div class="month">APR</div>
          <div class="day">19</div>
          <div class="dow">일</div>
        </div>
        <div class="race-info">
          <div class="race-badges">
            <span class="badge badge-full">FULL</span>
          </div>
          <div class="race-title">제17회 전국경제마라톤</div>
          <div class="race-meta">
            <span>📍 서울 여의도</span>
            <span>42K · 21K</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="race-right">
          <div class="d-day close">마감</div>
          <div>
            <div class="participants-bar"><div class="participants-fill" style="width:100%"></div></div>
            <div class="participants-text">마감</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 카드 6 -->
      <div class="race-card" onclick="showDetail()">
        <div class="race-date-box">
          <div class="month">APR</div>
          <div class="day">25</div>
          <div class="dow">토</div>
        </div>
        <div class="race-info">
          <div class="race-badges">
            <span class="badge badge-trail">TRAIL</span>
          </div>
          <div class="race-title">'SAFE KOREA' 제17회 대한경제마라톤대회</div>
          <div class="race-meta">
            <span>📍 경남 합천</span>
            <span>50K · 30K · 20K</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="race-right">
          <div class="d-day open">접수중</div>
          <div>
            <div class="participants-bar"><div class="participants-fill" style="width:33%"></div></div>
            <div class="participants-text">33%</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 카드 7 -->
      <div class="race-card" onclick="showDetail()">
        <div class="race-date-box">
          <div class="month">APR</div>
          <div class="day">25</div>
          <div class="dow">토</div>
        </div>
        <div class="race-info">
          <div class="race-badges">
            <span class="badge badge-half">HALF</span>
            <span class="badge badge-10k">10K</span>
          </div>
          <div class="race-title">2026 양인의 봄 양양철쭉마라톤</div>
          <div class="race-meta">
            <span>📍 강원 양양</span>
            <span>21K · 10K · 5K</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="race-right">
          <div class="d-day open">접수중</div>
          <div>
            <div class="participants-bar"><div class="participants-fill" style="width:60%"></div></div>
            <div class="participants-text">60%</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ══ SCREEN 2: 상세 ══ -->
  <div class="screen" id="screen-detail">
    <div class="detail-scroll">
      <div class="detail-hero">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513593771513-7b58b6c4af38?w=800&q=80" alt="레이스">
        <div class="detail-hero-overlay"></div>
        <div class="detail-back" onclick="showList()">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M15 18l-6-6 6-6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-wishlist" id="wishBtn" onclick="toggleWish()">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" id="wishIcon"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-hero-content">
          <h2>2026 장수트레일레이스 Spring</h2>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="detail-body">
        <div class="course-badges">
          <span class="course-badge-lg f">70K</span>
          <span class="course-badge-lg f">38K</span>
          <span class="course-badge-lg h">20K</span>
          <span class="course-badge-lg t">VK Kids</span>
        </div>

        <div class="course-tabs">
          <button class="course-tab active">신청하기</button>
          <button class="course-tab">공유하기</button>
        </div>

        <div class="info-grid">
          <div class="info-item">
            <div class="label">📍 장소</div>
            <div class="value">전북 장수 <small>장수황계경기장</small></div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item accent-border">
            <div class="label">📅 대회일</div>
            <div class="value">2026-04-03 <small>목요일</small></div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item">
            <div class="label">⏰ 출발시간</div>
            <div class="value">07:00 <small>AM</small></div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item">
            <div class="label">👟 참가비</div>
            <div class="value">70K <small>80,000원~</small></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <div class="section-title">접수 일정</div>
          <div class="timeline">
            <div class="tl-item">
              <div class="tl-dot done">✓</div>
              <div class="tl-content">
                <div class="tl-date">2026.01.02</div>
                <div class="tl-label">접수 시작</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-item">
              <div class="tl-dot done">✓</div>
              <div class="tl-content">
                <div class="tl-date">2026.01.15</div>
                <div class="tl-label">얼리버드 마감 (10% 할인)</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-item">
              <div class="tl-dot" style="border-color:rgba(232,240,0,.4);color:var(--accent);">→</div>
              <div class="tl-content">
                <div class="tl-date">2026.02.14 · <span style="color:var(--accent);font-weight:700;">D-50</span></div>
                <div class="tl-label">최종 접수 마감</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-item">
              <div class="tl-dot">🏁</div>
              <div class="tl-content">
                <div class="tl-date">2026.04.03</div>
                <div class="tl-label">대회 당일</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <div class="section-title">대회 소개</div>
          <div class="desc-box">
            <div class="desc-highlight">
              <span class="icon">🏔️</span>
              <div>노스페이스와 함께하는 2026 장수트레일레이스 Spring의 참가 접수 일정을 안내합니다.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="desc-highlight">
              <span class="icon">📋</span>
              <div><strong style="color:var(--accent);">RACE INFO</strong><br>일자: 2026.04.03 (목) ~ 05(금)<br>코스: 70K / 38K / 20K / VK / Kids<br>장소: 도보공원 3칸 및 장수군 일원 일대<br>참가기간: 2026.01.02(금) 14:00 OPEN</div>
            </div>
            <div class="desc-highlight">
              <span class="icon">🌟</span>
              <div>참가가 첫 선착을 넣는 순간 즐거이 즐거움을 추가해 드립니다. 가져오는 분, 러너한테 도움을 드리겠습니다.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <div class="section-title">문의</div>
          <a class="contact-row" href="#">
            <div class="contact-icon">✉️</div>
            <div class="contact-text">info@trailrunner.kr</div>
          </a>
          <a class="contact-row" href="#">
            <div class="contact-icon">📞</div>
            <div class="contact-text">063-353-2025</div>
          </a>
          <a class="contact-row" href="#">
            <div class="contact-icon">🌐</div>
            <div class="contact-text">trailrunner.kr</div>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div style="height:80px;"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-bar">
      <div class="cta-share">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="18" cy="5" r="3"/><circle cx="6" cy="12" r="3"/><circle cx="18" cy="19" r="3"/><line x1="8.59" y1="13.51" x2="15.42" y2="17.49"/><line x1="15.41" y1="6.51" x2="8.59" y2="10.49"/></svg>
      </div>
      <button class="cta-register">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="black" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        대회 신청하기
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ══ SCREEN 3: 캘린더 ══ -->
  <div class="screen" id="screen-calendar">
    <div class="cal-header">
